summary: Okay now I’m moving from upset and fusterated into livid. It took this shop almost eight weeks to tell me my order is not...
body:
Okay now I’m moving from upset and fusterated into livid. It took this shop almost eight weeks to tell me my order is not complete, an order that I still have not received but is heaven knows because I still have not received this order. An order that was placed more than almost two months - three months ago.

I realized this is not their fault but it is part of their image, and frankly bad business practices (or in my opinion)…the fact that there was not any type of communication until the shipment notification 3 weeks ago, and now this…why was this not communicated earlier.

Mainly cause this particular package had one item I am supposedly getting myself and the rest were/are gifts. Very late gifts for different people but now I feel such much disappointment that I have failed one with trying to do something nice for them and that I know this would have have been their first merch.

The only bright side is I did not let them know that I had placed an order so I can come up with something else now. However I’m pretty sure I’ve lost all faith in their shop.

But like I mentioned in another post, I’m not even sure if I have a right to complain as I’m in a position to even buy merch.
